[SCREENSHOT NOTE: rest-create-done.jpg]
This screenshot illustrates a terminal cURL POST request output to create an account:
curl -i -X POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/accounts -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"name":"John Doe","email":"john@doe.com"}'
Yields HTTP/1.0 201 CREATED status with correct JSON fields returned.
